"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-olympics-paris-2024-says-impact-of-global-cyber-outage-limited-ticketing-unaffected\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  PublishedJul 19, 2024, 06:48 PM  UpdatedJul 20, 2024, 05:14 PM  PARIS - The Paris Olympics organising committee said on Friday that a global cyber outage was slowing its operations, but the impact was limited and ticket sales were unaffected ahead of the Games which begin in a week.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.516245674771074e-13, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703097123, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The global tech outage that appeared to be related to issues at global cybersecurity firm CrowdStrike and Microsoft was affecting operations in many sectors on Friday including airports, airlines, media and banks.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CrowdStrike\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CrowdStrike\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CrowdStrike\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CrowdStrike\"}, {\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.9999983692523183, \"rank\": 1.3172578034674133e-06, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At this point, the impacts are limited and concern in particular the delivery of uniforms and accreditations,\\\" the Paris 2024 organising committee said, adding that they were in touch with people affected in order to postpone their visits to accreditation centres.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6625705869730907e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris 2024's ticketing systems have been unaffected.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The operations around the preparation of venues is continuing normally, and work schedules are not at risk.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The torch relay is continuing along its route as normal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Games' press centre, security checks outside were done manually using lists of names, and the accreditation desk was closed, a Reuters reporter said.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999949270659, \"rank\": 5.065246792854886e-09, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have arrived in Paris this morning and went to get my accredidation validated and have been told no,\\\" Sky Sports New Zealand journalist Wilson Catton said.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1404, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999957321961, \"rank\": 4.267863079463067e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1524, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"score\": 0.8789527649954327, \"rank\": 0.11571417559059137, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They can not issue any accreditation or anything for I do not know how long.\\\"\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tony Estanguet, the head of the Paris Olympics Organising Committee, told reporters that contingeny plans were put in place but the outage was slowing operations, and the committee was \\\"hoping that Microsoft can solve the outage very quickly.\\\"\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbp